---
import "../styles/solutionsGrid.scss"
---

<section id="solutionsGrid" class="bentogrid">

    <article class="bentoCol devCol radius border animatedBorder fadeUp" data-delay="0.25">

        <div class="colContent">

            <div class="colheading">

                <img src="/assets/icons/icon-development.svg" alt="Development Icon" loading="lazy" />

                <h3>Web Development</h3>

            </div> <!-- .colheading -->

            <p>We build fast, reliable websites and web apps using modern tools. Everything is designed to grow with your business and stay easy to manage over time.</p>
            
        </div> <!-- .colContent -->

        <img src="/src/assets/illustrations/web-development.svg" alt="Web Development Illustration" class="bentoImage" loading="lazy" />

    </article> <!-- .devCol -->

    <article class="bentoCol designCol radius border animatedBorder fadeUp" data-delay="0.5">

        <img src="/src/assets/illustrations/web-design.svg" alt="Web Design Illustration" class="bentoImage" loading="lazy" />

        <div class="colContent">

            <div class="colheading">

                <img src="/assets/icons/icon-design.svg" alt="Design Icon" loading="lazy" />

                <h3>Web Design</h3>

            </div> <!-- .colheading -->

            <p>We create custom designs that don't just look good — they're built to perform and align with your brand and business goals.</p>
            
        </div> <!-- .colContent -->

    </article> <!-- .designCol -->
    
    <article class="bentoCol apiCol radius border animatedBorder fadeUp" data-delay="0.25">

        <img src="/src/assets/illustrations/api-integration.svg" alt="API Integration Illustration" class="bentoImage" loading="lazy" />

        <div class="colContent">

            <div class="colheading">

                <img src="/assets/icons/icon-api.svg" alt="API Integration Icon" loading="lazy" />

                <h3>API Integrations</h3>

            </div> <!-- .colheading -->

            <p>We develop tailored solutions that connect your site to third-party APIs — enabling real-time data, automated workflows, and extended functionality.</p>
            
        </div> <!-- .colContent -->

    </article> <!-- .apiCol -->

    <article class="bentoCol wpCol radius border animatedBorder fadeUp" data-delay="0.5">

        <div class="colContent">

            <div class="colheading">

                <img src="/assets/icons/icon-refresh.svg" alt="Modernised WordPress Icon" loading="lazy" />

                <h3>Modernised WordPress</h3>

            </div> <!-- .colheading -->

            <p>Use WordPress as your content hub, but ditch the slow, clunky frontend. We connect it to a fast, modern framework — so you get the flexibility of WordPress with the performance of a next-gen site.</p>
            
        </div> <!-- .colContent -->

        <img src="/src/assets/illustrations/modernised-wordpress.svg" alt="Modernised WordPress Illustration" class="bentoImage" loading="lazy" />

    </article> <!-- .wpCol -->

</section> <!-- #solutionsGrid -->